     F*    ..FORD EDI(830) ALL USER DATA FILE ..                 *
     F*    K.OKACHI   2000.02.14                                 *
     F*    TCH        2000.05.26 ADD FI,MT RECORD                *
     F*    TCH        2000.05.30 ADD SHP,NOT,PER RECORD.RELEASE# *
     F*    TCH        2000.06.06 CALCULATE CUM                   *
     F*    TCH        2000.11.27 WHEN IT PROCESS,DOCK=BLANK      *
     F*    TCH        2001.02.14 USE ABF9P01 INSTEAD EDIPL30     *
     F*    TCH        2001.02.16 SAVE KEY DATA                   *
     F*    TCH        2001.05.21 SET NO DATA FLAG                *
     F*    TCH        2001.09.17 WHEN THERE IS NO WORKING DAY,   *
     F*                          ADD THE QTY TO THE PREVIOUS WEEK*
     F*    TCH        2001.11.07 CHANGE WSURY POSITON.           *
     F*               BECAUSE WSURY HAS OVERRIDDEN THE PREVIOUS  *
     F*               DATE FIELD.                                *
     F*    TCH        2001.12.05 TO AVOID THE DUPLICATE DATA IN
     F*                          ABFPP30,CHECK DATA BEFORE UPDATING.
     F* *IN10=1(NOT READ GADPL11)                                *
     F* *IN10=1(NOT READ AGDPL12)                                *
