     ******************************************************************
     C           KEY2      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           WTOKU   40
     C                     KFLD           WNONY   40
     C                     KFLD           WNKOJ   1
     C                     KFLD           #NUKE   4
     C                     KFLD           WSBAN   4
     C                     KFLD           WMHN1   5
     C                     KFLD           WMHN2   5
     C                     KFLD           WMHN3   5
     C                     KFLD           WMHN4   5
     C                     KFLD           @NYM
      * FOR ABFPP10(SETGT)
     C           KEY3      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           K32     5
     C                     KFLD           K33
     C                     KFLD           WCSDT
     C                     KFLD           K31
      * FOR ABFPP10(READPE)
     C           KEY7      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           K32
     C                     KFLD           K33
